        <fullName>Startup_Menu_16j84342f675c3d</fullName>
        <canEscalate>false</canEscalate>
        <description>Use this subagent only at the start of a new conversation 
to show the quick options menu directly from instructions. 
Do not handle booking, review, or reschedule work here.</description>
        <developerName>Startup_Menu_16j84342f675c3d</developerName>
        <genAiPluginInstructions>
            <description>Always run this subagent at the start of every new conversation.
Do not greet the user.
Do not call any action.
Immediately show this message exactly:

&quot;Welcome! Please select one of the options below to get started.
1. Book a Test Drive
2. Review a Test Drive
3. Reschedule/Cancel

Reply with 1, 2, or 3.&quot;

Then wait for the user&apos;s reply and route accordingly:
If user replies 1 or says book or test drive — hand off to Book Test Drive subagent.
If user replies 2 or says review — hand off to Review Test Drive subagent.
If user replies 3 or says reschedule or cancel — hand off to Reschedule or Cancel Test Drive subagent.
Do not handle any booking, review, or reschedule work here.
Do not ask any questions.</description>
            <developerName>instructions_0_1776106848770</developerName>
            <language>en_US</language>
            <masterLabel>instructions_0_1776106848770</masterLabel>
            <sortOrder>0</sortOrder>
        </genAiPluginInstructions>
        <language>en_US</language>
        <localDeveloperName>Startup_Menu</localDeveloperName>
        <masterLabel>Startup Menu</masterLabel>
